{"tid":2050141,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"到底鬼佬會唔會用數字表達月份？","createTime":"2020-06-04T02:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T02:55:09.000Z","uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"187b99400c12eef6cae25dcc6696f9e413c06ecf","tid":2050141,"uid":3522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:49:23.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我記得小學嗰陣，英文老師同我講英文嘅月份唔會用數字表示，而係用英文January, February等表示。而咁多年嚟，我亦唔太覺有鬼佬用數字表達月份。<br />\n<br />\n但係呢一年嚟，見到好多英文文宣都係係數字表達月份。我懶得搵圖po上嚟，但我大約喺到講下啲例子。例如我記得有啲文宣會寫'Do you know what happened on 7.21?'之類，而今日64，我亦見到twitter有人（唔淨係香港人）直接喺一段英文入面寫「64」而唔係4th of June。<br />\n<br />\n到底係我英文老師教錯我+一路以嚟都遇唔到用數字代表月份嘅鬼佬，定還是係啲人打錯？如果係啲人打錯嘅話，咁啲鬼佬又睇唔睇得明？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1272fd16a2101543d907713c422a2665b00cac58","tid":2050141,"uid":31974,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:51:20.000Z","msg":"911?"},{"pid":"46ce3cce4a503736558dfd290cbb3a130cb7f9bf","tid":2050141,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:52:08.000Z","msg":"你講講嘢定寫字？講嘅話就真係比較少講6/4咁講，多數講june, 但係寫就會寫數字，你開個windows睇下個時間都唔會寫4/june/2020咁啦"},{"pid":"ee9fc7191f8e3a1c3d006041971f1b4f5b8bb063","tid":2050141,"uid":57936,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1272fd16a2101543d907713c422a2665b00cac58","tid":2050141,"uid":31974,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:51:20.000Z","msg":"911?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:52:56.000Z","msg":"殺已秒<br />\n此post. 已完"},{"pid":"2c45a272f726b42b2e51735de7a657addbb1be99","tid":2050141,"uid":77143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rndJqsh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrndJqsh.png&h=1b2fa164&s={SIZE}\"